label: Strategic Basing
description:
Challenge:

How can we develop and evaluate data-informed basing options and generate options to realign missions to minimize job losses, as force structure changes to modernize the Air Force?

Value:

Support Air Force strategic decision-making by fusing data sources, automating analytic processes, using AI when appropriate, and deploying visualization tools to help AOs and senior leaders develop and defend COAs, and message the complex impacts their decisions will have across the Air Force and DoD.
